→ Identification of likely risks of material misstatement in the report,

→ Analytical procedures on selected disclosures in the report at Group level and at the level of the Industrial Businesses,

→ Inquiries and inspection of documents relating to the collection and reporting of selected data at Group level, at the level of the Industrial Businesses and at selected sites,

→ Inquiries of employees on material qualitative statements in the report as well as the inspection of selected under- lying documents,